Lfuns

I'm still writing this doc.
Lfuns are functions coded in the object that have a reserved name and task.
Wizards can code these functions themselves, and often do (i.e. reset).
Most used lfuns are:
reset
init
query_name
...

See also /doc/lfun and /doc/lfun/set&query
You'll get the idea...

Uglymouth
